The race will start at 06:30 tomorrow and a total of 5 000 athletes will participate in this ultra and half marathons.Participants can collect their race numbers at the following points:Ultra Marathon (at the municipal offices in Middelburg): 21 April from 12:00 till 20:00 22 April from 04:30 till 06:00 The race will start on 22 April at 06:00Wild Challenge (at the Damwal Complex): 21 April from 12:00 till 21:00 22 April from 05:00 till 06:30 The N11 between Middelburg and Loskopdam will be closed for traffic from 05:00 to 13:00.